{"tid":1249913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學生又比人煸動...","createTime":"2019-06-22T00:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T01:16:32.000Z","uid":150921,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"19702a1504c50cefa636774f98a7148d3596414f","tid":1249913,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 岩岩食早餐 又聽到兩個老野講<br />\nD學生又比人煸動 今次仲要圍警察 仲有法治既？<br />\n<br />\n由佔中聽撚到依家 成撚日話學生比人煸動<br />\n到底佢地係憑乜野覺得自己思考成熟過d學生？<br />\n呢班老野通常學歷唔高 成日持住自己年紀大<br />\n一副食鹽多過你食米既嘴樣<br />\n唔識客觀分析 直觀既感覺就係事實<br />\n<br />\n好心唔撚識就謙卑d啦 連最基本既事源都未了解過<br />\n你同佢解釋就話你候生 睇唔清<br />\n鬧鳩佢就無禮貌<br />\n<br />\n次次聽到呢句都㷫過火屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa867d16969b043f27d27a5cc6358e86ab09af0","tid":1249913,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:56:11.000Z","msg":"煽你老母咩 外國先唔想搞你 搞起上黎班官爭住帶路 幾時輪到班後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478ddd6e01ba2b25f64e3486449fee9b6978731a","tid":1249913,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:56:18.000Z","msg":"嘴臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f99ea14ab2989748523768d831739eb630f4f2","tid":1249913,"uid":130982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"煽動"},{"pid":"f1ad4e081a4534cfbffa1a5b1458ab4372601b8b","tid":1249913,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:57:12.000Z","msg":"所以咪有長輩圖既出現"},{"pid":"26cf2b768d3393f014c2f13ae27d4dfbf793bb3c","tid":1249913,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"d高宮仔女比人煽動到去美國讀書"},{"pid":"75228934486e82cd3b109e6c3144d8d4cb502f8e","tid":1249913,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f99ea14ab2989748523768d831739eb630f4f2","tid":1249913,"uid":130982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20